  <brief_title>Recombinant BNP on Heart and Renal Function in Acute Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Recombinant BNP on Heart and Renal Function in Acute Decompensated Heart Failure Patients With Acute Renal Injury</official_title>
  <sponsors>
